<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-z3gLpd7yknf1YoNbCzqRKc4qyor8gaKU1qmn+CShxbuBusANI9QpRohGBreCFkKxLhei6S9CQXFEbbKuqLg0DA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/userpage.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="top">
        <div class="title"><p class="head">!deabook</p></div>
        <div class="options">
            <div class="bar">
                <a class="b1" href="about"><button class="b2">About</button></a>
                <a class="b1" href="delete"><button class="b2">Delete Account</button></a> 
            </div>
            <div class="bar">
                <a class="b1" href="http://localhost:8080/home/newidea"><button class="b2">New Idea</button></a>
                <a class="b1" href="http://localhost:8080/home"><button class="b2">Log Out</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="data">
        <div class="display">
            <% for(user of users){%>
                <div class="profile">
                    <div class="dp">
                        <div class="us"><p class="letter"><%=user.username[0]%></p></div>
                        <!-- <div class="cam">
                        <i id="dpCam" class="fa-solid fa-camera"></i>
                        </div> -->
                    </div>
                    <p class="name"><%=user.username%></p>
                </div>
            <%}%> 
            <div class="yourIdea">
                <div class="idea">
                    <p>Your All Idea Is Here</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="allIdea">
                <div class="posts">
                    <p class="postedIdea"><p class="bold">...$...</p>"Twenty years from now you will be more disappointed by the things that you didnâ€™t do than by the ones you did do."</p>
                </div>
                <div class="posts">
                    <p class="postedIdea"><p class="bold">...$...</p>"My friends, love is better than anger. Hope is better than fear. Optimism is better than despair. So let us be loving, hopeful and optimistic. And we'll change the world."</p>
                </div>
                <% for(post of posts){%>
                <div class="posts">
                    <p class="postedIdea"><p class="bold">...$...</p><%=post[0]%></p>
                </div>
                <%}%>
            </div>
            
            
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="idea.js"></script>
</body>
</html>